{"tid":1544910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屌黑狗記者會以後用英文問問題 既可以等外媒明 又可以班藍絲唔撚明","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T18:02:32.000Z","uid":4322,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"379ae12e50a787f326a208233b7d6b61570e069b","tid":1544910,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">既可以等全世外媒知佢地幾柒 <br />\n又等班藍絲唔撚明 要等重播！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中文班撚樣易spin好多 外媒未必明白哂 用英文外媒唔使搵第二手資料！ </span></strong></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一定要迫佢地用英文答！！！畀全界知有幾柒！！！</strong></span></span><br />\nExample:<br />\n<br />\n港台英文女記者今（5日）幸獲警察公共關係科警司高振邦揀選發問，指高的上司、高級警司江永祥一方面批評市民戴面罩或匿名指控他們濫權，惟其一眾同事執勤時，卻未有清楚展示其警員編號、委任證和面容，令投訴人無從辨別其身份，難以投訴，反問警方為何不樹立榜樣（role model），執勤時在制服上清楚展示警員編號，以及不戴面罩，以供識別。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥回應時反駁記者，指警察執勤時是否清楚展示其編號、委任證和面容，與市民戴面罩或匿名無理地指控他們無關，僅重申根據內部指引，警察執勤時須展示其編號或委任證。記者追問他下次會否在例行記者會，向公眾示範警察會在制服上哪位置，展示其編號或委任證，以及有哪些特徵可供識別，加強公眾信心。江僅點頭然後指示身旁的上司、總警司謝振中回答餘下提問，有如聽不到記者的追問。謝Sir對此都呆一呆，與江Sir對望一下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190905&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60012901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190905%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60012901&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=37b4379b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190905%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60012901&h=e2b93d14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190905&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60012901</a>"},{"pid":"731e7d8735a1f1a15593fbca9e0dffee61a80398","tid":1544910,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f142ff9023a2333beb0c36a41c363a1f4ed0ac5a","tid":1544910,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc0fd6fd9477e2f7307065da6360172e080c2fd6","tid":1544910,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"我要班撚樣出醜！！"},{"pid":"59d58863b52ba25a0671d8b7e7cfe801f3c4a841","tid":1544910,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:20:17.000Z","msg":"同毅進仔講英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2abc55680313a65cd0fd064a462123aebca16f","tid":1544910,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:22:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40bcf73088cb55d2c6c95a95ab47c2b8c23eda81","tid":1544910,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy